dcterms:description: A dataset containing patches of tissue images from 19 different sites annotated for 5 different cell classes (Epithelial, Neoplastic, Necrotic, Inflammatory, and Connective) with a total of over 200,000 nuclear level annotations. The dataset is used for training models to classify tumor patches in pathology images.
